Package: socrata.com
Title: Socrata Open Data Discovery and Access Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Socrata Discovery API and SODA 2.1.
    Search across thousands of open data portals, browse datasets by domain,
    fetch metadata, and retrieve actual data rows with SoQL queries. All
    functions return tibbles.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports: httr2, jsonlite, dplyr, tibble
